---
description: Pointers to reusable agent prompts and where outputs live
alwaysApply: false
---

When the user says **accessibility audit**, **user scenario**, **release gate**, or
**architecture review**, open `docs/agent-build-checklist.md` § "Agent prompt library"
and follow the matching prompt. Each prompt must produce a **dated artifact**, not just
chat output:

- accessibility audit → `accessibility/audits/YYYY-MM-DD-*.md` (update `accessibility/wcag-tracker.md`)
- user scenario → `docs/scenarios/YYYY-MM-DD-*.md` + an integration/UI test
- release gate → check against `specs/feature-flags.md` + `docs/release/release_checklist.md`
- architecture review → read-only summary; multi-phase plans go in `ongoing/` (index in `ongoing/README.md`)
